text.tspan: Share of population with mental or substance disorders, male vs.
Share of males vs. females with any mental health or substance use disorder; this includes depression, anxiety, bipolar, eating
disorders, schizophrenia, alcohol and drug use disorders, and neurodevelopmental disorders. Due to the widespread
under-diagnosis, these estimates use a combination of sources, including medical and national records, epidemiological data,
Data source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease
